<br>
No old world items have more then 1 augment slot, no slot 8 type augments are even sold on any vendor, thus screwing people with PoTime gear. Frankly, for people in high end gear already, especially potime gear, there are NO upgrades in LDoN unless you RAID.<br>
<br>
Which also means that all the Points we obtain are useless since we cannot buy ANY augments for our armor. Why should I even bother doing 90% of the content if I can't use the points for Anything? <br>
<br>
And about raids, the points you do get from a raid is Less then what you get from a 6man dungeon crawl, and these raids are by no means a joke. And along with that, we will be lucky if we even get 2 augments out of a raid, and you can only do 1 raid per theme every 5 days. So in a 5day week, you'd be lucky to get 10 augments for a 36 man raid.<br>
<br>
Realize every character has 20-21 Armor slots, and you're looking at a fuckton of augments to satisfy your raid.<br>
<br>
<br>
So basically, LDoN isn't worth jack shit to any guild serious about raiding until Sony adds some more buyable augments that can go in slot 1, 4 , and 8 , which don't suck ass. Unfortunatly, the slot 1 augments will NEED to be made to suck since the LDoN armor would be able to become too uber if given those same augments. So for 99% of the server population, all of you're current gear will need to settle for +6 agi, str, wis, int, and so forth, until you start spending points on LDoN armor  (which usually isnt much better then Luclin/Velious armor when max augments are applied).<br>
<br>
If you have Elemental armor or better, you're screwed.. period.<br>
